enchantment.slu.apocalypse_upgrade.desc: extra damage increases by 8 per enchant level. (drop from minecraft lord)
enchantment.slu.armor_piercing.desc: Cause 8% armor negation damage and heal 50% of armor negation damage.
enchantment.slu.blessing.desc: when attacked every 16 seconds, get resistance buff for 1(+enchant level) seconds and get 2.4(+enchant level) HP.
enchantment.slu.courage.desc: If use same weapon on both hands, get 4.5 extra attack damage.
enchantment.slu.critical_hit.desc: Cause extra damage every 6 seconds. (9 + 3% of entity max health)
enchantment.slu.demonization.desc: Get 2 attack damage per enchant level.
enchantment.slu.frost_attack.desc: cause extra 2.5 damage and slow the target for 3 seconds.
enchantment.slu.giant_slayer.desc: Cause extra damage to monster. (3 + 2% of entity max health)
enchantment.slu.grasp_of_undying.desc: Cause 8 extra damage every 4 seconds and get 3 health.
enchantment.slu.ignition.desc: Burn monster and cause extra damage.
enchantment.slu.rage.desc: Cause extra damage. (10% of player's lost health)
enchantment.slu.shadow_attack.desc: Cause extra damage every 12 seconds. (4 + 100% of entity armor point)
enchantment.slu.ultimate_magic.desc: Cause 16 extra damage every 5 seconds and get shield for 4 seconds.
enchantment.slu.venom.desc: Make entity unhealable for 4 seconds with 15% chance.
